lyTime":"2016-12-12T07:44:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>數學好正<br />\n有根有據每樣野都有邏輯連起</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChing 呢個世界好似樣樣野都有<br />\n得中共好似冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db54dfaa0302504f7bba17e7c2b601db08980ed3","tid":35565,"uid":21937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:48:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平心而論 你地學完真係訓練到邏輯思維？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪又係頹下頹下係度計啲計完又計<br />\n型式重複又重複既題目<br />\n未學過M1 M2唔知係點<br />\n但係覺得用講野 寫野 訓練邏輯性 強過用數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n數學又唔只數字 只不過數字係最清楚表達邏輯 唔同語言 比較多bias同埋maths有一part係discrete maths 一堆logic同 algorithm 都係用到數學黎表達文字既logic更加清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dca8f00e8355db060d8b3e278a971b48e8d6e2e","tid":35565,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:49:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平心而論 你地學完真係訓練到邏輯思維？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪又係頹下頹下係度計啲計完又計<br />\n型式重複又重複既題目<br />\n未學過M1 M2唔知係點<br />\n但係覺得用講野 寫野 訓練邏輯性 強過用數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係個syllabus寫得唔好，唔係學數學無用，好多嘢無解，剩係教人用，大學engine/apply數都有類似問題，所以難啲令人觸類旁通，睇唔到最直觀嘅概念，而呢啲概念我個人覺得係最有用，利申唔係讀數學，唔敢班門弄斧"},{"pid":"affa5cedff1cfe0b4158b4e3dbee9d33e9880e50","tid":35565,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:54:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平心而論 你地學完真係訓練到邏輯思維？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪又係頹下頹下係度計啲計完又計<br />\n型式重複又重複既題目<br />\n未學過M1 M2唔知係點<br />\n但係覺得用講野 寫野 訓練邏輯性 強過用數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中學雞數嗰啲就唔好拎嚟講啦，中學數頂多只係叫「算術」<br />\n<br />\n要了解數學點樣訓練邏輯思維，可以接觸一下Axiomatic set theory、Category theory、Abstract Algebra、Topology等等高等數學"},{"pid":"f157e124343dab1111a2f742069dde22a28ec4a7","tid":35565,"uid":63568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:55:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平心而論 你地學完真係訓練到邏輯思維？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪又係頹下頹下係度計啲計完又計<br />\n型式重複又重複既題目<br />\n未學過M1 M2唔知係點<br />\n但係覺得用講野 寫野 訓練邏輯性 強過用數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n數學又唔只數字 只不過數字係最清楚表達邏輯 唔同語言 比較多bias同埋maths有一part係discrete maths 一堆logic同 algorithm 都係用到數學黎表達文字既logic更加清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但對我地日常生活真係冇乜意義<br />\n呢個亦都係一直問緊點解數學要係必修咁悲哀既位"},{"pid":"57c721168681989f3f489ed5aa702c9e6e691a97","tid":35565,"uid":33508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T07:57:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平心而論 你地學完真係訓練到邏輯思維？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪又係頹下頹下係度計啲計完又計<br />\n型式重複又重複既題目<br />\n未學過M1 M2唔知係點<br />\n但係覺得用講野 寫野 訓練邏輯性 強過用數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本你做到搵到個flow就唔洗再係咁做<br />\n考試年年都唔同你唔用腦做100百次都冇用<br />\n同埋數學同算術係有分別嫁"},{"pid":"0f8e83d34080d7459d089